    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set sail in <i>Wyrd Waters</i>, a <strong>tactical online multiplayer</strong> naval experience where strategy meets mythological chaos! Build custom fleets of fantastical <strong>Anglo-Saxon-inspired ships</strong>, each with their own quirks and playstyles. <u><strong>Strategize, cooperate or betray your friends,</strong></u> and face off across multiple rounds to determine the true victor!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gather your Crew</strong></i> - <i>Wyrd Waters</i> is built for <strong><u>2–8 players</u></strong>, so when that sixth friend hops on the call, <i>you'd better have your fleet ready!</i> <strong><u>Mac, Linux, and Steam Deck users? You're covered too.</u></strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Fleet</strong> – Choose from <strong>9 uniquely fantastical ships</strong>. Get close enough for <strong>RAM</strong>ming or channel the thunder of Thor and <strong>pray you don't blow yourself up</strong>. There's a ship for your style.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/5f2907116bb0db82adc766335648377b.poster.avif?t=1750435307\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/5f2907116bb0db82adc766335648377b.webm?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/5f2907116bb0db82adc766335648377b.mp4?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn Your Strategy</strong> – <i>More isn't always better.</i> <strong>Every ship is controlled individually</strong>! Will you command an armada or master one deadly vessel?</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the Maps</strong> – <i>Battle across 6 varied maps, each with unique layouts, hazards, and secrets.</i> Keep your eyes on the <strong>Fog of War</strong> and the kraken beneath it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/2eed7918ff27fc6a0ed587cb031ae7ea.poster.avif?t=1750435307\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/2eed7918ff27fc6a0ed587cb031ae7ea.webm?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/2eed7918ff27fc6a0ed587cb031ae7ea.mp4?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for Survival</strong> – Time your cooldowns, line up your shot, or hide. Only one sailor walks away.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progress with Runes</strong> – Spend the spoils of victory to unlock new ships, maps, and skins. Your style, your fleet, your legend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/eca97a079c0066bfbeb539e32d9009a0.poster.avif?t=1750435307\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/eca97a079c0066bfbeb539e32d9009a0.webm?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001570/extras/eca97a079c0066bfbeb539e32d9009a0.mp4?t=1750435307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the crew!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist</strong> <i>Wyrd Waters</i> now on Steam and be the first to conquer the seas when the game launches! Don’t miss out on updates, community events, and special playtests—<strong>join our Discord</strong> for all the latest news.</p>",
